Paul Le Person https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Le_Person 0 Paul Le Person (10 February 1931 in Argenteuil – 8 August 2005) was a French actor of Breton origin. He appeared in more than ninety films from 1963 to 2005. Paul_Le_Person ( 10_February_1931 in Argenteuil – 8_August_2005 ) was a_French_actor of Breton_origin . He appeared in more_than_ninety_films from 1963 to 2005 .
